dct_description_sm: Taxlot parcel boundaries for Mason County, Washington, 2009. This dataset has multiple originators. The WhoCreated attribute field specifies the originator. For parcels with the ESU attibute, please refer to the parts of this metadata file specific to Inside Oregon Enterprises, Engineering Support Unit. For parcels with the Whiteshield attribute, please refer to the parts of this metadata file specific to WhiteShield, Inc.
